  "title": "star-rating cannot work with float values",
  "body": "When ratings are in the form of 3.2 3.8 4.1 then the star-rating widget cannot work because it's adding refinements like \"rating = 2\" or \"rating = 3\".\n\nI wonder if we could use numeric filters? Maybe not because we want the counts for each rating, is that it?\n",
